flavour_text:
A legendary bird
POKéMON that is
said to appear to doomed people who
are lost in icy
mountains.
name: articuno

flavour_text:
A legendary bird
POKéMON that is
said to appear from clouds while
dropping enormous
lightning bolts.
name: zapdos

flavour_text:
Legendary bird
POKéMON. It is
said to migrate from the south
along with the
spring.
name: moltres

flavour_text:
It was created by
a scientist after
years of horrific gene splicing and
DNA engineering
experiments.
name: mewtwo

flavour_text:
The rain clouds it
carries let it
fire thunderbolts at will. They say
that it descended
with lightning.
name: raikou

flavour_text:
Volcanoes erupt
when it barks. Un­
able to restrain its extreme power,
it races headlong
around the land.
name: entei

flavour_text:
솟아나는 물의 부드러움이 깃들어 있는 포켓몬이다.
흐르는 듯한 몸놀림으로 대지를 달려
탁해진 물을 맑게 하는 힘을 지녔다.
name: suicune

flavour_text:
It is said that it
quietly spends its
time deep at the bottom of the sea
because its powers
are too strong.
name: lugia

flavour_text:
Legends claim this
POKéMON flies the
world's skies con­ tinuously on its
magnificent seven-
colored wings.
name: ho-oh

flavour_text:
Known as “The Being of Knowledge.”
It is said that it can wipe out the
memory of those who see its eyes.
name: uxie

flavour_text:
Known as “The Being of Emotion.”
It taught humans the nobility of
sorrow, pain, and joy.
name: mesprit

flavour_text:
Known as “The Being of Willpower.”
It sleeps at the bottom of a lake
to keep the world in balance.
name: azelf

flavour_text:
It has the power to control time.
It appears in Sinnoh-region myths
as an ancient deity.
name: dialga

flavour_text:
It has the ability to distort
space. It is described as a deity
in Sinnoh-region mythology.
name: palkia

flavour_text:
It dwells in volcanic caves. It
digs in with its cross-shaped feet
to crawl on ceilings and walls.
name: heatran

flavour_text:
밧줄로 묶은 대륙을
당겨서 움직였다고 하는
전설이 남아 있다.
name: regigigas

flavour_text:
A Pokémon that is said to live in a
world on the reverse side of ours.
It appears in an ancient cemetery.
name: giratina-altered

flavour_text:
Shiny particles are released from
its wings like a veil. It is said
to represent the crescent moon.
name: cresselia

flavour_text:
REGIROCK was sealed away by people
long ago. If this POKéMON’s body is
damaged in battle, it is said to seek out suitable rocks on its own to repair
itself.
name: regirock

flavour_text:
REGICE’s body was made during an ice
age. The deep-frozen body can’t be
melted, even by fire. This POKéMON controls frigid air of
minus 328 degrees F.
name: regice

flavour_text:
REGISTEEL has a body that is harder
than any kind of metal.
Its body is apparently hollow. No one has any idea what this POKéMON
eats.
name: registeel

flavour_text:
LATIAS is highly sensitive to the
emotions of people. If it senses any
hostility, this POKéMON ruffles the feathers all over its body and cries
shrilly to intimidate the foe.
name: latias

flavour_text:
LATIOS has the ability to make its foe
see an image of what it has seen or
imagines in its head. This POKéMON is intelligent and
understands human speech.
name: latios

flavour_text:
KYOGRE has the power to create massive
rain clouds that cover the entire sky
and bring about torrential downpours. This POKéMON saved people who were
suffering from droughts.
name: kyogre

flavour_text:
GROUDON has long been described in
mythology as the POKéMON that raised
lands and expanded continents. This POKéMON took to sleep after a
cataclysmic battle with KYOGRE.
name: groudon

flavour_text:
RAYQUAZA lived for hundreds of millions
of years in the earth’s ozone layer,
never descending to the ground. This POKéMON appears to feed on water
and particles in the atmosphere.
name: rayquaza

flavour_text:
Un Pokémon légendaire qui a combattu
les humains pour protéger les Pokémon.
Il est d’un naturel calme et posé.
name: cobalion

flavour_text:
Il a combattu les humains pour protéger
les Pokémon ayant perdu leur foyer à
cause de leurs guerres fratricides.
name: terrakion

flavour_text:
Legends say this Pokémon
confounded opponents with
its swift movements.
name: virizion

flavour_text:
Le bas de son corps est entouré d’une
masse d’énergie semblable à un nuage.
Il vole dans le ciel à 300 km/h.
name: tornadus-incarnate

flavour_text:
Les terres qu’il a survolées sont
recouvertes d’innombrables traces
des éclairs qu’il y a fait tomber.
name: thundurus-incarnate

flavour_text:
Un Pokémon mythique.
Il projette de sa queue un tourbillon
de flammes capable de tout emporter.
name: reshiram

flavour_text:
Sa queue produit de l’électricité.
Il dissimule son corps dans un nuage
électrique et plane dans le ciel d’Unys.
name: zekrom

flavour_text:
Il fait fructifier les cultures partout
où il passe, c’est pourquoi on l’appelle
“le dieu des moissons”.
name: landorus-incarnate

flavour_text:
Son corps produit une énergie à très
basse température, mais le souffle
glacé qu’il exhale l’a gelé lui-même.
name: kyurem

flavour_text:
えいえんの　いのちを　わけあたえると
いわれている。じゅもくの　すがたで
１０００ねん　ねむり　ふっかつする。
name: xerneas

flavour_text:
つばさと　おばねを　ひろげて　あかく
かがやくとき　いきものの　いのちを
すいとる　でんせつの　ポケモン。
name: yveltal

flavour_text:
Lorsque l’écosystème de Kalos est menacé,
ce Pokémon apparaît et utilise son mystérieux pouvoir.
name: zygarde

flavour_text:
こうきしんおうせいな　メレメレの
まもりがみ。　かみなりぐもを　よび
いかずちを　からだに　ためこむ。
name: tapu-koko

flavour_text:
むじゃきで　ざんこくな　アーカラの
まもりがみ。　はなの　かぐわしい
かおりが　エネルギーの　みなもと。
name: tapu-lele

flavour_text:
たいぼくを　ひきぬき　ブンブン
ふりまわす。　くさきを　しげらせて
そのエネルギーを　きゅうしゅうする。
name: tapu-bulu

flavour_text:
Although it’s called a guardian deity, terrible
calamities sometimes befall those who
recklessly approach Tapu Fini.
name: tapu-fini

flavour_text:
はかない　ガスじょうの　からだ。
たいきの　チリを　あつめながら
ゆっくりと　せいちょうしていく。
name: cosmog

flavour_text:
しんだように　まったく　うごかないが
ふれると　ほのかに　あたたかい。
おおむかしは　ほしのマユと　よばれた。
name: cosmoem

flavour_text:
べつせかいに　すむと　いわれる。
ぜんしんから　はげしいひかりを　はなち
やみよも　まひるのように　てらすのだ。
name: solgaleo

flavour_text:
コスモッグが　しんかした　♀だと
いわれる。　だい３の　めが　うかぶとき
べつせかいへと　とびさっていく。
name: lunala

flavour_text:
ちかで　ねむりに　ついていたようだ。
たいこに　べつせかいから　やってきたと
おもわれる　ＵＢらしき　せいぶつ。
name: necrozma

flavour_text:
でんせつの　えいゆうと　よばれる
ポケモン。　きんぞくを　とりこみ
ぶぐに　へんかさせ　たたかう。
name: zacian-hero

flavour_text:
ひとのおうと　ちからを　あわせ
ガラルを　すくった　ポケモン。
きんぞくを　とりこみ　たたかう。
name: zamazenta-hero

flavour_text:
むねの　コアが　ガラルちほうの
だいちから　わきだす　エネルギーを
きゅうしゅうして　かつどうしている。
name: eternatus

flavour_text:
きびしい　たんれんを　つみ　わざを
みがく。　たいとくした　わざによって
しんかしたときに　すがたが　かわる。
name: kubfu

flavour_text:
いちげきひっさつが　しんじょう。
あいての　ふところに　とびこみ
きたえられた　こぶしを　たたきこむ。
name: urshifu-single-strike

flavour_text:
でんきエネルギーの　かたまり。
からだの　リングを　はずすと　ひめた
ちからが　ときはなたれるらしい。
name: regieleki

flavour_text:
うでの　かたちは　こだいの　ドラゴン
ポケモンの　あたまという　がくせつも
あるが　しょうめいされていない。
name: regidrago

flavour_text:
ひづめから　きょうりょくな　れいきを
はなつ。　ほしいものは　なんでも
ちからずくで　うばう　あばれんぼう。
name: glastrier

flavour_text:
しかく　いがいの　ごかんを　つかい
ようすを　さぐる。　けられたものは
たましいを　ぬかれてしまうという。
name: spectrier

flavour_text:
いやしと　めぐみの　ちからを　もつ
じあいに　みちた　ポケモン。　はるか
むかし　ガラルに　くんりんしていた。
name: calyrex
